McElroy’s largest machine in the TracStar lineup has everything the operator needs to fuse 16in OD to 48in OD (450mm to 1200) pipe efficiently and effectively. The TracStar 1200 is a self-contained, remote-controlled vehicle that is equipped with an onboard generator. This is a huge benefit since it eliminates having to transport an external power source. It’s also incredibly easy to manoeuvre on almost any job site, with its self-propelled rubber crawler tracks that can handle rough terrain and grades up to 30%. For ease of mobility, freedom of movement and getting the job done right, there’s nothing like the TracStar. Here’s what you get with a TracStar 1200: